      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  초기화
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN.
      *@1 초기화

      *@1.1 출력영역확보 파라미터 및 결과코드 초기화
           INITIALIZE    WK-AREA
                         XIJICOMM-IN
                         XZUGOTMY-IN

      *@1.2 출력영역 확보
           #GETOUT       YPJL4027-CA

      *@1.3 COMMON AREA SETTING 공통IC프로그램 호출
      *    고객번호
           MOVE YNJL4027-KB-PIN        TO AACOM-CUST-IDNFR

           #DYCALL IJICOMM YCCOMMON-CA XIJICOMM-CA

      *@1.4 호출결과 확인
           IF COND-XIJICOMM-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XIJICOMM-R-ERRCD
                     XIJICOMM-R-TREAT-CD
                     XIJICOMM-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  입력값검증
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S2000-VALIDATION-RTN.
      *@2 입력값검증

      *@2.1 처리구분CHECK
      *@실행조건:YNJL4027-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01
      *@처리내용:처리구분 "01" 아닐경우 오류처리한다
      *@에러메시지:처리구분 오류입니다
      *@조치메시지:전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다.
           IF YNJL4027-PRCSS-DSTIC NOT = CO-CHA-01
              #ERROR CO-B3000070 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF
           .
       S2000-VALIDATION-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  업무처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.
      *@3 업무처리

           INITIALIZE    XDJL4027-IN

      *@3.1 입력파라미터 조립
      *@처리내용:처리DC입력파라미터=
      *@SET(처리구분,차주번호,기준년월일)
           MOVE YNJL4027-PRCSS-DSTIC   TO XDJL4027-I-PRCSS-DSTIC
           MOVE YNJL4027-KB-PIN        TO XDJL4027-I-KB-PIN
           MOVE YNJL4027-BASE-YMD      TO XDJL4027-I-BASE-YMD

      *@3.2 프로그램 호출
      *@처리내용:DC프로그램호출
           #DYCALL DJL4027 YCCOMMON-CA XDJL4027-CA

      *@3.3 처리결과CHECK
      *@실행조건:COND-XDJL4027-OK
      *@처리내용:리턴코드가 정상(00) 아닐경우 오류처리한다
           IF COND-XDJL4027-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XDJL4027-R-ERRCD
                     XDJL4027-R-TREAT-CD
                     XDJL4027-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  출력처리
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S6000-OUTPUT-RTN.
      *@4 출력처리

      *@4.1 출력항목 조립
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-DBTRZ-NAME
             TO YPJL4027-DBTRZ-NAME
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-MGT-CLAM
             TO YPJL4027-MGT-CLAM
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME
             TO YPJL4027-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD
             TO YPJL4027-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
             TO YPJL4027-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD
             TO YPJL4027-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME
             TO YPJL4027-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT
             TO YPJL4027-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD1
             TO YPJL4027-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD1
