           MOVE XDJL4027-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT
             TO YPJL4027-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT
      * 2011.06.03최종적용포괄한도　추가
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT
             TO YPJL4027-LAST-INLS-LIMT

      *@4.2 출력라인수 조립
           MOVE XDJL4027-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
             TO YPJL4027-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

      *@4.3 그리드1 조립
      *@실행조건:WK-I > YPJL4027-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1
      *@처리내용:그리드1 조립
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL   WK-I > YPJL4027-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

                   MOVE XDJL4027-O-GRID1(WK-I)
                     TO YPJL4027-GRID1(WK-I)
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S6000-OUTPUT-EXT.
           EXIT.
